who want to see Xian'er today?

853
00:53:15,400 --> 00:53:17,239
Those who watched the princess grow up

854
00:53:17,679 --> 00:53:19,880
all want to see Mr. Fan.

855
00:53:20,480 --> 00:53:21,800
The Empress Dowager

856
00:53:22,159 --> 00:53:23,239
also wants to see him.

857
00:53:23,599 --> 00:53:25,760
But she'll see him after lunch.

858
00:53:27,079 --> 00:53:27,840
Who should we visit first?

859
00:53:28,440 --> 00:53:29,400
Madam, since you're here,

860
00:53:29,559 --> 00:53:32,280
you certainly should
visit Consort Yi first.

861
00:53:33,000 --> 00:53:33,920
What about the empress?

862
00:53:34,159 --> 00:53:35,800
Her Majesty doesn't feel well today.

863
00:53:36,079 --> 00:53:37,159
We'd better not disturb her.

864
00:53:39,960 --> 00:53:40,639
This way, please.

865
00:53:46,440 --> 00:53:48,000
I know you've been
to the Imperial Study,

866
00:53:48,320 --> 00:53:49,920
but this is the real imperial harem.

867
00:53:50,440 --> 00:53:51,400
Don't look around.

868
00:53:51,800 --> 00:53:53,440
You might be accused of

869
00:53:53,440 --> 00:53:54,360
being disrespectful and discourteous.

870
00:53:55,440 --> 00:53:57,000
Madam, you know Consort Yi?

871
00:53:57,639 --> 00:53:59,119
She's my cousin.

872
00:53:59,880 --> 00:54:01,760
The imperial family
has been gracious to my family.

873
00:54:02,239 --> 00:54:03,719
Then why do you marry my dad?

874
00:54:03,719 --> 00:54:04,519
For what?

875
00:54:05,039 --> 00:54:05,800
Whatever makes me happy!

876
00:54:06,199 --> 00:54:07,800
I see. For love.

877
00:54:08,679 --> 00:54:10,400
Don't be too arrogant
when you see Her Highness later.

878
00:54:11,199 --> 00:54:13,199
I see. I should save your face.

879
00:54:13,800 --> 00:54:15,800
Consort Yi is the birth mother
of the Third Prince.

880
00:54:16,039 --> 00:54:16,800
Don't be disrespectful.

881
00:54:17,079 --> 00:54:18,719
Isn't the Crown Prince the third eldest
among the princes?

882
00:54:19,079 --> 00:54:19,960
According to the tradition
of our dynasty,

883
00:54:20,320 --> 00:54:21,559
the Crown Prince won't be included

884
00:54:21,559 --> 00:54:22,840
when ranking other princes.

885
00:54:23,440 --> 00:54:25,800
Though Consort Yi's son is still a kid,

886
00:54:26,280 --> 00:54:28,079
he's the Third Prince.

887
00:54:28,920 --> 00:54:30,320
That means

888
00:54:30,880 --> 00:54:32,760
the Crown Prince doesn't deserve to

889
00:54:33,199 --> 00:54:34,599
have any family or brother.

890
00:54:35,159 --> 00:54:36,119
How dare you say that?

891
00:54:38,199 --> 00:54:39,159
Madam, how long has it been

892
00:54:39,159 --> 00:54:40,119
since you last saw Consort Yi?

893
00:54:41,280 --> 00:54:42,119
It's been four years.

894
00:54:42,159 --> 00:54:42,800
It's so long!

895
00:54:44,039 --> 00:54:44,760
After she married
into the imperial family,

896
00:54:44,840 --> 00:54:46,320
we seldom see each other.

897
00:54:46,760 --> 00:54:48,119
Is Consort Yi cold by nature?

898
00:54:49,400 --> 00:54:50,719
Big and profound as the Liu family,

899
00:54:50,960 --> 00:54:52,039
if we visit Consort Yi frequently,

900
00:54:52,719 --> 00:54:54,239
we might be suspected of collusion.

901
00:54:55,239 --> 00:54:56,039
In this sense,

902
00:54:56,280 --> 00:54:58,840
the palace walls actually
become her cage.

903
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:01,119
Indeed.

904
00:55:13,719 --> 00:55:15,239
How hard-hearted are you

905
00:55:15,440 --> 00:55:16,199
to leave me here

906
00:55:16,199 --> 00:55:17,280
to rot by myself.

907
00:55:17,440 --> 00:55:19,079
I actually have no one to talk to.

908
00:55:19,599 --> 00:55:21,159
After all, the Liu family
is related to Your Highness by blood.

909
00:55:21,400 --> 00:55:22,719
We should avoid suspicion.

910
00:55:23,079 --> 00:55:24,599
You belong to the Fan family now.

911
00:55:24,679 --> 00:55:25,960
Why worry about this?

912
00:55:26,400 --> 00:55:27,679
Aren't I here today?

913
00:55:28,400 --> 00:55:29,920
Weren't it for Fan Xian's marriage

914
00:55:29,920 --> 00:55:31,159
with Wan'er,

915
00:55:31,599 --> 00:55:33,960
I wonder when could we

916
00:55:34,239 --> 00:55:35,480
actually meet.

917
00:55:38,280 --> 00:55:39,400
You must be Fan Xian.

918
00:55:42,280 --> 00:55:44,440
Nephew Fan Xian
pays respects to Auntie Liu.

919
00:55:47,079 --> 00:55:49,679
Mr. Fan, you should call Your Highness.

920
00:55:49,920 --> 00:55:51,000
You must be respectful.

921
00:55:53,440 --> 00:55:54,880
He's really a good lad.

922
00:55:56,480 --> 00:55:57,679
Fan Xian and others

923
00:55:57,880 --> 00:55:59,159
have arrived in Consort Yi's palace.

924
00:56:03,159 --> 00:56:04,400
Is Liu Ruyu with him?

925
00:56:04,679 --> 00:56:05,239
Yes.

926
00:56:08,039 --> 00:56:09,199
Haven't seen her for years,

927
00:56:09,880 --> 00:56:11,760
Consort Yi must be happy.

928
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,119
I heard that Fan Xian
called Her Highness

929
00:56:14,440 --> 00:56:15,599
Auntie Liu directly
regardless of formalities.

930
00:56:16,360 --> 00:56:17,920
Consort Yi smiled happily.

931
00:56:18,400 --> 00:56:19,119
It's not detected

932
00:56:19,320 --> 00:56:20,760
till now.

933
00:56:22,840 --> 00:56:24,039
After seeing so many formalities,

934
00:56:24,719 --> 00:56:25,960
one would long
for family affection instead.

935
00:56:26,800 --> 00:56:28,199
Fan Xian is really smart

936
00:56:29,239 --> 00:56:29,960
by calling her that.

937
00:56:31,480 --> 00:56:33,280
Who will he visit next?

938
00:56:33,880 --> 00:56:34,559
I've asked.

939
00:56:35,159 --> 00:56:36,679
He will visit Imperial Consort Shu

940
00:56:36,800 --> 00:56:37,639
and Lady Ning successively.

941
00:56:38,199 --> 00:56:38,920
After the lunch,

942
00:56:39,280 --> 00:56:40,519
the Empress Dowager will see him.

943
00:56:42,480 --> 00:56:43,400
Send someone to follow him.

944
00:56:43,760 --> 00:56:45,280
Tell me what he says.

945
00:56:47,039 --> 00:56:48,920
Imperial Consort Shu and Lady Ning

946
00:56:48,920 --> 00:56:49,840
are still waiting.

947
00:56:50,159 --> 00:56:50,920
After the lunch,

948
00:56:51,119 --> 00:56:53,440
the Empress Dowager also
wants to see Mr. Fan.

949
00:56:56,840 --> 00:56:57,320
Auntie Liu,

950
00:56:58,440 --> 00:56:59,440
