958
00:57:10,599 --> 00:57:11,280
Never mind!

959
00:57:12,480 --> 00:57:13,599
Madam, stay with Auntie Liu.

960
00:57:13,800 --> 00:57:14,599
I'll be fine.

961
00:57:15,239 --> 00:57:16,440
Ruoruo, stay here, too.

962
00:57:16,960 --> 00:57:18,480
Drink some tea and eat some snacks.

963
00:57:20,039 --> 00:57:21,280
I'll go with my brother.

964
00:57:22,159 --> 00:57:23,760
Just be careful.

965
00:57:24,079 --> 00:57:25,320
When you visit other consorts,

966
00:57:25,840 --> 00:57:27,199
