The Second Prince is funny.

972
00:57:41,840 --> 00:57:43,360
I wonder what his mother would be like.

973
00:57:43,679 --> 00:57:44,480
Among all the consorts,

974
00:57:44,559 --> 00:57:46,119
Imperial Consort Shu
is the most rigorous,

975
00:57:46,480 --> 00:57:47,599
