You're probably fooled by him.

1032
01:00:30,000 --> 01:00:31,000
He's shrewd and deep.

1033
01:00:32,519 --> 01:00:34,280
He never hits it off
with others at first meeting.

1034
01:00:38,360 --> 01:00:41,079
I will say no more about him.

1035
01:00:42,559 --> 01:00:43,760
You'll see

1036
01:00:45,039 --> 01:00:46,320
after knowing him for a long time.

1037
01:00:48,880 --> 01:00:49,440
There's one thing

1038
01:00:49,440 --> 01:00:50,480
you probably don't know.

1039
01:00:51,920 --> 01:00:52,639
I...

1040
01:00:54,519 --> 01:00:55,599
love reading.

1041
01:00:59,159 --> 01:00:59,840
I know! I know!

1042
01:01:00,079 --> 01:01:01,480
I already know that.

1043
01:01:02,320 --> 01:01:03,239
You're a younger member of the family.

1044
01:01:03,920 --> 01:01:04,719
I should give you presents

1045
01:01:05,320 --> 01:01:06,920
