1046
01:01:07,679 --> 01:01:09,119
I'm never fond of vulgar things.

1047
01:01:09,360 --> 01:01:12,079
So I'll give you some ancient books
and unique copies.

1048
01:01:12,320 --> 01:01:13,760
But I don't know what you like.

1049
01:01:13,760 --> 01:01:14,599
Actually, I...

1050
01:01:14,599 --> 01:01:15,719
Yet, even if you tell me what you want,

1051
01:01:15,880 --> 01:01:17,800
I might be unwilling
to give them to you.

1052
01:01:19,239 --> 01:01:20,199
Just let me pick some books

1053
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:22,519
for you.

1054
01:01:26,119 --> 01:01:26,639
That's fine.

1055
01:01:27,480 --> 01:01:29,079
It won't be convenient for you
to hold the books.

1056
01:01:29,280 --> 01:01:31,239
I'll have them sent
to Consort Yi's palace.

1057
01:01:31,679 --> 01:01:33,960
Take them when you leave. OK?

1058
01:01:34,480 --> 01:01:35,440
Your Highness, you're so considerate.

1059
01:01:52,079 --> 01:01:53,320
Do you have anything else?

